(1. Create a Stripe account at stripe.com if not done yet.) Tj
T* (2. Copy your real test keys from Stripe Dashboard > Developers > API Keys.) Tj
T* (3. In .env set: STRIPE_SECRET_KEY, STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY, STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET.) Tj
T* (4. Run: node scripts/setup-stripe.js to auto-create all 5 plan products and prices.) Tj
T* (5. The script will print the 10 IDs Ś paste them into .env.) Tj
