(The Stripe checkout route \(src/app/api/stripe/checkout/route.ts\) reads STRIPE_SECRET_KEY to initialize the SDK and then reads per-plan price IDs) Tj
T* (from STRIPE_STARTER_PRICE_ID, STRIPE_GROWTH_PRICE_ID, STRIPE_PROFESSIONAL_PRICE_ID, STRIPE_BUSINESS_PRICE_ID,) Tj
T* (STRIPE_ENTERPRISE_PRICE_ID. The subscribe page \(/shop/subscribe\) calls POST /api/stripe/checkout which creates a Stripe Checkout Session) Tj
T* (and redirects the user to hosted Stripe payment page. After payment Stripe calls POST /api/stripe/webhook which flips the shop's Subscription) Tj
T* (record in the database to status=active and sets the plan. Without these keys: clicking "Subscribe" throws a 500, no subscription record is ever) Tj
T* (created, and the shop is permanently locked at the subscription gate.) Tj
