T* (urgent alert \(shop home\). The service worker \(public/sw.js\) subscribes using NEXT_PUBLIC_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY. /api/push/subscribe stores the) Tj
T* (subscription endpoint in the database. /api/push/send sends the notification. Without VAPID keys the subscription call fails and no notifications are) Tj
T* (ever delivered.) Tj
